Class AltDiffusionPipeline: pipeline for text-to-image generation using Alt Diffusion. It integrates VAE, text encoder, tokenizer, UNet, scheduler, safety checker, feature extractor. Provides loading methods for textual inversion, LoRA, checkpoint, IP adapters. Handles encoding prompts, latents, decoding, guidance, safety checking.

Business intent: enable developers to generate images from textual prompts using Alt Diffusion model, with safety filtering and support for fine-tuning extensions.

Keywords: text-to-image, diffusion, pipeline, VAE, UNet, scheduler, safety checker, LoRA, textual inversion, IP adapter, prompt encoding, latent decoding, guidance, image generation.
